lead_paragraph: Bobby Ryan scored twice, including the game-winner at 2:33 of overtime, to lift the Ottawa Senators to a 3-2 victory over the St. Louis Blues on Monday night.

headline.print_headline: Ryan Scores 2, Gets OT Winner to Lift Senators Past Blues
